content.rendered:
Directed by Nishanth Kalidindi

Written by Vivekanand Kalaivanan. Nishanth Kalidindi

Star Vasanth Selvam (Periya Pandi). Vijay Ram (Chikku Pandi). Hakkim Shah (Johan Arza). Dinesh Mani (Ila Pandi). Augustin (Andrew). Vijay Sethupathi (Lorry Driver)

Language Tamil. Malayalam

Producers Aneesh Chand. Hestin Jose Joseph. Tom Joseph. Nishanth Kalidindi. Chakravarthy Ramachandra. S. Sashikanth. Vinoth Thanigasalam. Jijo Thomas. Srinivas Varma

Production Y Not Music. Y Not Studios
